### Staff Management API - REST Client
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api/v1
@contentType = application/json

### 1. GET All Staff
GET {{baseUrl}}/staffs
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 2. CREATE New Staff
POST {{baseUrl}}/staff/add
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "username": "johndoe",
  "mobileNumber": "01712345678",
  "permissions": {
    "createInvoice": true,
    "editInvoice": true,
    "deleteInvoice": false,
    "cashmemo": true,
    "uploadReport": false
  },
  "isActive": true
}

### 3. CREATE Staff with Full Access
POST {{baseUrl}}/staff/add
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Admin User",
  "username": "adminuser",
  "mobileNumber": "01812345678",
  "permissions": {
    "createInvoice": true,
    "editInvoice": true,
    "deleteInvoice": true,
    "cashmemo": true,
    "uploadReport": true
  },
  "isActive": true
}

### 4. GET Single Staff by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/staff/698c432ab24c050d9011686f
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 5. GET Staff by Username
GET {{baseUrl}}/staff/username/johndoe
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 6. GET Active Staff Only
GET {{baseUrl}}/staff/active/list
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 7. GET Staff with Specific Permission (Create Invoice)
GET {{baseUrl}}/staff/permission/createInvoice
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 8. GET Staff with Specific Permission (Delete Invoice)
GET {{baseUrl}}/staff/permission/deleteInvoice
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 9. GET Staff with Specific Permission (Cashmemo)
GET {{baseUrl}}/staff/permission/cashmemo
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 10. UPDATE Staff
PUT {{baseUrl}}/staff/edit/698c432ab24c050d9011686f
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "John Doe Updated",
  "username": "johndoe",
  "mobileNumber": "01712345679",
  "permissions": {
    "createInvoice": true,
    "editInvoice": true,
    "deleteInvoice": true,
    "cashmemo": true,
    "uploadReport": true
  },
  "isActive": true
}

### 11. UPDATE Single Permission
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/staff/698c432ab24c050d9011686f/permissions
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "permission": "deleteInvoice",
  "value": true
}

### 12. UPDATE Single Permission (Disable)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/staff/698c432ab24c050d9011686f/permissions
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "permission": "uploadReport",
  "value": false
}

### 13. DEACTIVATE Staff
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/staff/698c432ab24c050d9011686f/deactivate

### 14. ACTIVATE Staff
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/staff/698c432ab24c050d9011686f/activate

### 15. DELETE Staff (Hard Delete)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/staff/698c432ab24c050d9011686f
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

